channel.title: Interleaved RSS Feed
channel.description: This is an interleaved feed of the most recent entries from each RSS source, skipping any feeds with errors.

item.title: WATCH: Hamas Supporter Attacks Pro-Israel Protester, Ends Up Shot in the Stomach
Fani Willis likely to defy Georgia state Senate subpoena ahead of hearing Friday, chairman says
item.description: District Attorney Fani Willis is expected to defy a Georgia state senate subpoena for her testimony ahead of a hearing Friday, Fox News has learned.

item.title: Charlamagne Tha God Dunks on Biden For Wearing Trump Hat
item.description: Charlamagne tha God on Thursday called President Joe Biden the "donkey of the day" for wearing a Trump campaign hat during an appearance in Shanksville, Pennsylvania, on Wednesday, The Hill reported.

item.title: Post-Debate Poll Explains Harris' Big Problem, Why Trump Is Now Leading in Michigan
House GOP rolling out bill to block China from accessing US ports
item.description: FIRST ON FOX: GOP Rep. Michelle Steele is rolling out a bill to block China and other American adversaries from accessing U.S. ports.

item.title: Rep. McCaul Moves to Hold Blinken in Contempt
item.description: House Foreign Affairs Committee Chair Michael McCaul, R-Texas, is moving forward with a resolution to hold Secretary of State Antony Blinken in contempt over his failure to comply with a subpoena regarding the withdrawal from Afghanistan three years ago.

item.title: Trump, Speaking in Arizona, Lays Out Big Plans - But He'll Need a GOP Congress
'It'll upend the community': PA town roiled by talk of migrant housing in Civil War-era orphanage building
item.description: An organization linked to a Civil War-era orphanage property has sought to host about 1,000 unaccompanied migrant minors, according to local lawmakers and correspondence.

item.title: Fla. County Returns Once-Banned Books to Shelves
item.description: One county in Florida is returning once-banned books to library shelves, following the settlement of a federal lawsuit, reports Politico.

item.title: Trump Promises Policies to Help Families Keep More Cash in Their Pockets, Buy a Home in Tucson Speech
'Very scary territory': Libertarian Party president fears what Harris could do to American Dream
item.description: Angela McArdle, president of the National Libertarian Party, told Fox News Digital she was not surprised by the results of a survey that showed only 9% of American voters think the American Dream is more attainable today.

item.title: Trump Proposes Ending Taxes on Overtime Pay
item.description: Former President Donald Trump said Thursday he would move to end taxes on overtime pay if he wins in November.

item.title: The Presidential Debate Shows Us Why Alternative Media Is Saving America
Gov. Newsom signs bill to resume harsh penalties for smash-and-grab robberies in California
item.description: California Gov. Gavin Newsom signed a bill Thursday that brings back harsh penalties for those who commit smash-and-grab retail thefts and other robberies.

item.title: A Review of Tevi Troy's 'The Power and the Money'
item.description: History buffs, especially political history buffs, will want to pick up Tevi Troy's latest book, "The Power and the Money."
